{"word":"G1195 - δεσμεύω - desmeúō - des-myoo'-o - Bind","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δεσμεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">desmeúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">des-myoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bind</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கட்டு"},{"paragraph":"to put in chains, to bind up, bind together"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a (presumed) derivative of <a href=\"#/G1196 - δεσμέω - desméō - des-meh'-o/1196\">G1196</a>; to <i>be a binder</i> (<i>captor</i>), that is, to <i>enchain</i> (a prisoner), to <i>tie on</i> (a load): - bind.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}